msgstr "`stork-core` 提供了实现自定义注册器所需的 Stork API 和 SPI。 `stork-configuration-generator` 会在构建时根据注册器提供程序上的注解生成配置类。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Custom Service Registrar Provider"
