#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Stork uses a provider model.\n"
"To create a custom registrar, you need two classes:"
msgstr "Stork 采用提供者模式。要创建一个自定义注册器，你需要两个类："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A *provider* implementing `ServiceRegistrarProvider` — the factory that creates registrar instances."
msgstr "一个实现 `ServiceRegistrarProvider 的` *提供程序* ——用于创建注册器实例的工厂。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A *registrar* implementing `ServiceRegistrar` — the actual registration logic."
msgstr "一个实现 `ServiceRegistrar 接口的` *注册器* ——即实际的注册逻辑。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Let's start with the provider.\n"
"Create the `src/main/java/org/acme/services/CustomServiceRegistrarProvider.java` file with the following content:"
msgstr "我们先从提供者开始。创建 `src/main/java/org/acme/services/CustomServiceRegistrarProvider.java` 文件，内容如下："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "There are a few important things to note:"
msgstr "有几点需要注意："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `@ServiceRegistrarType` annotation declares the registrar _type_.\n"
"This is the value used in the `quarkus.stork.<service-name>.service-registrar.type` property.\n"
"Here, it is `custom`."
msgstr "`@ServiceRegistrarType` 注解用于声明注册器 _类型_ 。该值将用于 `quarkus.stork.<service-name>.service-registrar.type` 属性中。此处，该值为 `custom` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `@ServiceRegistrarAttribute` annotations declare the configuration attributes for this registrar.\n"
"Stork's annotation processor (provided by `stork-configuration-generator`) uses these annotations to generate\n"
"the `CustomRegistrarConfiguration` class at compile time. You do not need to write this class yourself."
msgstr "`@ServiceRegistrarAttribute` 注解用于声明该注册器的配置属性。Stork 的注解处理器（由 `stork-configuration-generator` 提供）会在编译时利用这些注解生成 `CustomRegistrarConfiguration` 类。您无需自行编写该类。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `@ApplicationScoped` annotation makes this provider a CDI bean, so Stork can discover it automatically."
msgstr "`@ApplicationScoped` 注解使该提供程序成为一个 CDI Bean，因此 Stork 可以自动发现它。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `createServiceRegistrar` method is the factory that creates a `CustomServiceRegistrar` from the generated configuration."
msgstr "`createServiceRegistrar` 方法是一个工厂方法，用于根据生成的配置创建一个 `CustomServiceRegistrar` 。"

