#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Now let's implement the registrar itself.\n"
"Create the `src/main/java/org/acme/services/CustomServiceRegistrar.java` file with the following content:"
msgstr "现在让我们来实现注册器本身。创建 `src/main/java/org/acme/services/CustomServiceRegistrar.java` 文件，内容如下："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This registrar:"
msgstr "该注册商："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Receives its configuration (host and port) from the generated `CustomRegistrarConfiguration` class."
msgstr "从生成的 `CustomRegistrarConfiguration` 类中获取其配置（主机和端口）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Stores registered instances in a `ConcurrentHashMap`."
msgstr "将实例存储在 `ConcurrentHashMap` 中。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/stork-manual-service-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Implements `registerServiceInstance` to add a service instance to the map."
msgstr "实现 `registerServiceInstance` 方法，用于将服务实例添加到映射中。"

#. type: Plain text
